<h3>SECTION 3 – BECOMING A CHARTER MEMBER</h3>
<h4>RULES OF CONDUCT</h4>
Charter Members promise to:
<ol>
  <li>Handle themselves and their operations and conduct as a Charter Member honestly, morally and legally.</li>
  <li>Keep their activities honorable to reflect well on themselves and on Digitanzo.</li>
  <li>Speak well of Digitanzo, as well as competitors.</li>
  <li>Honestly present the product and offering in keeping with what is set forth in the Digitanzo literature.</li>
  <li>Explain the Compensation Plan honestly and completely as set forth in the Digitanzo corporate materials.</li>
